<see></see>
</indexterm>

The <tt?>%install</tt?> script is the third script RPM executes during a
build.  As the name implies, it is normally used to install the software.
The commands in the script can be any valid <tt?>sh</tt?> commands.

<figure id="sc-rpm-specref-">
<title>*** Enter New Title Here ***</title>
<screen width="60">
%install
</screen>
